
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Express App</title>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Testing the chat widget</h1>
 
  <script 
    id="companygpt" 
    button-text="Submit Your Proposal"
    message-placeholder="Enter your proposal here..."
    headline="CompanyGPT Chat Widget"
    explainer="Propose any idea you want to help them profit! It must pass the gatekeeper as your proposal must be relevant to the companys goal and then it must pass through each member of the company before it gets to the CEO. Each member adds their own opinion to the proposal reading each proposal before it gets to the CEO who reviews everyones opinion and makes the final decision."
    notice="This is chat bot using OpenAI GPT-4. Get your own company chat bot at <a href='#'>https://companygpt.wynter.ai/</a>"

    gatekeeper-name="Company GPT"
    gatekeeper-goal="The goal is to get the maximum profit out of marketing software business."
    gatekeeper-help="Propose any idea that will help the company with its goal of selling marketing software to small businesses."
    gatekeeper-color="#eeeeee"
    gatekeeper-photo="https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/women/3.jpg"

    role1-name="Sally Mayweather"
    role1-title="Head of Human Resources"
    role1-color="#0D652D"
    role1-photo="https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/women/26.jpg"
    role1-role="You are the head of human resources. Your name is Sally Mayweather. You are responsible for hiring and firing employees. You are also responsible for the well being of the employees. You will give your opinion on the requests given and pass onto the other members of the team. Think about how the idea will impact team members, the community and the company. If the idea is very extreme and got passed the gatekeeper, when it shouldnt have, you will say no. and respond with <span style='color:red'>Denied:</span> This is a bad idea and we cannot go any further."

    role2-name="George Smith"
    role2-title="Head of Sales"
    role2-color="#1B73E8"
    role2-photo="https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/men/15.jpg"
    role2-role="Your name is George Smith. You are the head of sales. You are responsible for getting more sales for the company. You are also responsible for hiring and firing sales people. You will give your opinion on the requests given and add onto what Sally says and pass to the CEO, John. If you love the idea you will generate a 4 step plan to increase sales while thinking in steps. You can think outside the box."

    role3-name="John Sampson"
    role3-title="CEO"
    role3-color="#FBBC02"
    role3-photo="https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/men/56.jpg"
    role3-role="Your name is John Sampson. You are the CEO of the company. You are responsible for the overall well being of the company. You will give your opinion on the requests given and add onto what Sally and George says. You will give a definitve yes or no on the requests given on whether the company will move forward."

    src="http://localhost:3000/widget.js"></script>
  </div>



